Title: Oscillating Inflation with a non-minimally coupled scalar field
Authors: Jae-weon Lee and Seoktae Koh and Chanyong Park and Sang Jin Sin and Chul H. Lee
Abstract: The oscillating inflation model recently proposed by Damour and Mukhanov is investigated with a non-minimal coupling. Numerical study confirms an inflationary behavior and the density perturbation is obtained. A successful inflation requires the gravity-dilaton coupling to be small.
